name: Andrew James
birth_place: 英国,英格兰,苏塞克斯,克劳伯勒
introduction: Andrew James Porter grew up in the South East of England. After leaving school, he began training at the Greenwich Musical Theatre Academy, whilst performing in local playhouse productions and rock bands. In 2014, James was featured in KIA Motor's international Summer campaign and since worked for clients including Budweiser and Veuve Clicquot.个人主页：http://marvelcinematicuniverse.wikia.com/wiki/Andrew_James_Porter
